swagger-ui-dist@5.32.11

Vendored (not npm-installed) for Task 39's self-hosted /docs page — see
scripts/build.ts (copies swagger-ui-bundle.js + swagger-ui.css into
dist/web/docs-assets/) and packages/api/src/index.ts's GET /docs route.
Only swagger-ui-bundle.js and swagger-ui.css are needed: the bundle's
built-in BaseLayout renders the full spec explorer, including "Try it
out", without swagger-ui-standalone-preset.js (that file only adds the
top navbar / URL-entry UI, which this deployment doesn't use since the
spec URL is hardcoded to /openapi.json).

To update: download swagger-ui-dist from npm, verify the version, and
replace swagger-ui-bundle.js + swagger-ui.css here (LICENSE/NOTICE are
Apache-2.0, from the same package).
